      "writtenOn": "2021-06-30T20:00:18Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Why not make `linkify` return `template.HTML` instead of `string` (and make it call template.HTMLEscapeString inside)? It is the standard way to denote that something has already been escaped.",
